List have increased the campaign contributions from women, women
still don't give nearly as much money _ or as often _ as men. But
that could change. By Mary Leonard. 1400 words.
</P>
<P>
   NAVY-ANTHRAX (Undated) _ Zachary Johnson is willing to throw
away his Navy career rather than take the anthrax vaccine. Aug. 16
he becomes the first person in the Navy to face a court-martial for
refusing to submit to the shots. By Ellen Barry. 1200 words.
</P>
<P>
