<SLUG> BC-QUAYLE-2000-HNS </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
QUAYLE SAYS HE'S IN THE 2000 RACE TO WIN 
</HEADLINE>
   (EDS: Filed in ``w'' and ``p'' categories)  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients.)  
 By DAN FREEDMAN  
 c.1999 Hearst Newspapers  
