<P>
   OFFICE-SAFETY (Washington) _ The transformation from industrial
to information society has not defused the fight between labor and
management over occupational safety. An example is to be offered in
the House Wednesday, when Republicans and Democrats battle over
federal safety standards for white-collar and service economy
workers. By Eun Lee Koh. 900 words.
