<P>
   NATIONAL NEWS (``a'' category)
</P>
<P>
   ZAPRUDER-FILM (Dallas) _ Arbitrators declare that the government
must pay the heirs of Abraham Zapruder $16 million for the
26-second strip of film that Zapruder took of the assassination of
President John F. Kennedy in 1963. By JIM HENDERSON. (Already
filed.)
</P>
