<P>
   NIXON-SPOOF (Los Angeles) _ Two clueless teen girls contribute
to Richard Nixon's downfall ``Dick,'' an imaginative satire. By Bob
Strauss.
</P>
<P>
   DICK-REVIEW (Los Angeles) _ Review of ``Dick.'' 3 stars
</P>
